title: Icon
body:
Hey, i still didnt get the icon from playing with bots(players), and i played about 5 games and won 4 :D. 

Just asking when im getting it :DDD{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}

replies.body: Not the Demacia icon, the blue brain one im talking about

The Demacia icons are still being given out, and should all be delivered by April 20th. Keep checking your notifications, and if you don't have the icon by then feel free to reach out to us in a ticket!
